column22: dbgap Can only documentation if drag the file into excel. Information seems scattered in this site. While the tabs are helpful, for the study tab you need to scroll through a lot of information (e.g. it took a few minutes to locate where the dates of the studies were). The Public download site is particularly difficult to navigate (lots of folders with nonstandardized file names). The repository does, however, give you a brief preview of the data (i.e. number of participants, study type, etc.).
